define.name: VAULT_E_ALREADYOPENED
define.abstract: The IENOVIVaultDocument was already opened by this transaction, you are supposed to close it before re-open.

define.name: VAULT_E_CLIENTFILEACCESSDENIED
define.abstract: The ENOVIVault Client object has not enought right to access to the given input file.

define.name: VAULT_E_CLIENTFILECANTACCESS
define.abstract: The ENOVIVault Client object can't access to the given input file.

define.name: VAULT_E_CLIENTFILECANTCREATEORTRUNCATE
define.abstract: The ENOVIVault Client object has not enought right to access to the given input file.

define.name: VAULT_E_CLIENTFILENOTFOUND
define.abstract: The ENOVIVault Client object wasn't able to find the given input file.

define.name: VAULT_E_CLOSEFILEFAILED
define.abstract: The close operation on a file failed.

define.name: VAULT_E_INCOMPATIBLEOPENMODE
define.abstract: The requested open mode is not compatible with the current open mode.

define.name: VAULT_E_INVALIDOPENMODE
define.abstract: The submitted open mode is not a valid open mode.

define.name: VAULT_E_INVALIDTRANSACTION
define.abstract: The submitted transaction is not a valid transaction.

define.name: VAULT_E_JDBCDRIVERLOADFAILED
define.abstract: Unable to load the JDBC driver.

define.name: VAULT_E_MAXDBCONNREACHED
define.abstract: Max number of database connection reached.

define.name: VAULT_E_MEDIUMFULL
define.abstract: There is not enough disk space to save the file.

define.name: VAULT_E_MODIFYBYANOTHERTRANSACTION
define.abstract: The IENOVIVaultDocument was already opened by antoher transaction.

define.name: VAULT_E_MOVEFILEFAILED
define.abstract: The move operation on a file failed.

define.name: VAULT_E_NOMASTER_REF
define.abstract: Master Vault Client references are invalid.

define.name: VAULT_E_NOUSERSESSION_FOUND
define.abstract: There was no ENOVIVault Document corresponding to the given oid.

define.name: VAULT_E_NOVAULTDOCUMENT_DELETED
define.abstract: The IENOVIVaultDocument corresponding to the given oid was deleted.

define.name: VAULT_E_NOVAULTDOCUMENT_FOUND
define.abstract: There was no IENOVIVaultDocument corresponding to the given oid.

define.name: VAULT_E_NOVAULTDOC_FOUND
define.abstract: There was no ENOVIVault Document corresponding to the given oid.

define.name: VAULT_E_OPENEDBYANOTHERTRANSACTION
define.abstract: The IENOVIVaultDocument was already opened by antoher transaction.

define.name: VAULT_E_OPENEFILEFAILED
define.abstract: The open operation on a file failed.

define.name: VAULT_E_READFILEFAILED
define.abstract: The read operation on a file failed.

define.name: VAULT_E_REFVAULTDOCUMENT_MISSINGPARAMETERS
define.abstract: Some parameters on the reference IENOVIVaultDocument we need in order to perform the operation are missing.

define.name: VAULT_E_REFVAULTDOCUMENT_NOTVALUATED
define.abstract: The reference IENOVIVaultDocument has no value associate with it, so there is nothing to associate.

define.name: VAULT_E_SEEKFILEFAILED
define.abstract: The seek operation on a file failed.

define.name: VAULT_E_VAULTDOCUMENTNOTOPEN
define.abstract: The IENOVIVaultDocument object is not open in spite of it is supposed to be opened.

define.name: VAULT_E_VAULTDOCUMENT_MISSNIGPARAMETERS
define.abstract: Some parameters on the IENOVIVaultDocument we need in order to perform the operation are missing.

define.name: VAULT_E_VAULTDOCUMENT_NOTVALUATED
define.abstract: The IENOVIVaultDocument has no value associate with it, so there is nothing to associate.

define.name: VAULT_E_WRITEFAULT
define.abstract: The write operatioin was not completed due to a disk error.

define.name: VAULT_E_WRITEFILEFAILED
define.abstract: The write operation on a file failed.
